w340_casperjs_wordpress_install: install wordpress using casperjs
=================================================================

Install WordPress using CasperJS script

Configuration
=============

$ sed -i s/dbval/xxx/g install.js		# database
$ sed -i s/urlval/yyy/g install.js		# site url
$ sed -i s/titleval/Blog Title/g install.js	# title

Example
=======

$ cd path/to/wordpress/dir
$ chmod 777 .	# apache should have rights to create wp-config.php
$ db/install	# configure database
$ ./install.js
$ chmod 755 .

Reference
=========

CasperJS
http://casperjs.org
